      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid)<strong> </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>sausage meat</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the pan and cook for 5 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1688730080108-x200.jpg",
